<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>BMS EATS</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sevillana&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Amatic+SC:wght@400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
 
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/flash')  %>
    <nav class="navbar sticky-top navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"><img src="/images/logo.png" alt="" width="40" height="40"></a>
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup"
          aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
          <div class="navbar-nav">
            <a class="nav-link active" href="">Home</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/menu">Menu</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/cart">Cart</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container-fluid justify-content-end">
        <button
          type="button"
          class="btn btn-danger"
          style="
            --bs-btn-padding-y: 0.25rem;
            --bs-btn-padding-x: 0.5rem;
            --bs-btn-font-size: 1rem;
          "
        >
          <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">LOGOUT</a>
        </button>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <section id="hero" class="hero section dark-background">
      <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide carousel-fade">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
          <button
            type="button"
            data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
            data-bs-slide-to="0"
            class="active"
            aria-current="true"
            aria-label="Slide 1"
          ></button>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
            data-bs-slide-to="1"
            aria-label="Slide 2"
          ></button>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
            data-bs-slide-to="2"
            aria-label="Slide 3"
          ></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img
              src="/images/canteen14.jpg"
              class="d-block w-100"
              alt="..."
              style="height: 100vh"
            />
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <span id="heading"> <h3>LAW CANTEEN</h3></span>
              <p>
                Law school life got you stressed and fried? Law canteen's the
                perfect place to hide. Recharge, refuel, and conquer the day,
                one delicious bite at a time.
              </p>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/menu">ORDER NOW</a>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="/images/canteen15.jpg"
              class="d-block w-100"
              alt="..."
              style="height: 100vh"
            />
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <span id="heading"> <h3>VIDYARTHI KHANA</h3></span>
              <p>
                From the irresistible aroma of crispy samosas to the comforting
                warmth of masala chai, the Vidyarthi Khana is a student's
                culinary paradise.
              </p>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/menu">ORDER NOW</a>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="/images/canteen16.jpg"
              class="d-block w-100"
              alt="..."
              style="height: 100vh"
            />
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <span id="heading"> <h3>SIP AND SNACK</h3></span>
              <p>
                The ultimate burger and fry destination. Get ready to sink your
                teeth into juicy patties and crispy golden fries that will leave
                you craving for more.
              </p>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/menu">ORDER NOW</a>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button
          class="carousel-control-prev"
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide="prev"
        >
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button
          class="carousel-control-next"
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide="next"
        >
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="about-us">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to BMS EATS! We are dedicated to providing you with the best
          food and service on campus. Our canteens are designed to be your go-to
          spots for a quick bite, a relaxed meal, or a place to hang out with
          friends. Whether you're in need of a pick-me-up between classes or a
          full meal, we've got you covered. Our team is committed to quality and
          customer satisfaction. Come visit us and experience the difference!
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="p-3 mb-2 bg-dark text-white">
        <span id="footer"
          ><p>&copy; 2024 BMS EATS. All rights reserved.</p></span
        >
        <div class="footer-details">
          <div class="container-fluid justify-content-left">
            <p>
              CONTACT US:<img
                src="/images/phone.png"
                alt="Cart Icon"
                width="20"
                height="20"
              />
              8867196461
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="container-fluid justify-content-left">
            <span id="email">
              <P
                >EMAIL US:
                <img src="/images/mail.png" alt="Cart Icon" width="20" height="20" />
                bmsceats@bmsce.ac.in</P
              >
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
  <script
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  ></script>
</html>
